### 创建支付回调超时 Incident
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "payment-service 支付回调超时",
  "serviceName": "payment-service",
  "endpoint": "/api/payment/callback",
  "source": "DEMO",
  "traceId": "trace-payment-timeout-001",
  "exceptionType": "TimeoutError",
  "summary": "5 分钟内 500 错误率升高，p95 延迟升至 3200ms"
}

### 启动 Workflow
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/start-workflow
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询 Workflow 节点
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/1/nodes

### 查询 Incident 列表
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents

### 查询 Incident 详情
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1

### 查询 Workflow 实例
GET http://localhost:8080/api/workflows/1

### 以下为后续 Day 5 / Day 7 接口，当前阶段尚未实现

### 查询处置方案
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/actions

### 标记线下已执行
POST http://localhost:8080/api/actions/1/mark-offline-executed
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "executor": "sre-demo",
  "resultDetail": "已在线下通过值班系统开启延迟重试，本系统只记录处理结果"
}

### 查询模拟指标
GET http://localhost:8080/api/demo/metrics/1

### 生成复盘
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/generate-postmortem
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 查询复盘
GET http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/postmortem

### 关闭 Incident
POST http://localhost:8080/api/incidents/1/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "closedBy": "demo-user",
  "comment": "指标恢复，复盘已生成"
}
